TM TT LUN VN THC S
ti: Nghin cu ng dng cng ngh IoT trong h thng quan trc mi trng
Tc gi lun vn: Nguyn Vit Qu Kha: 2020B
Ngi hng dn: TS. Phm Ngc Hng
T kha (Keyword): h thng quan trc mi trng, IoT platform, kin trc
microservices, thit b IoT Data Logger, ESP32.
Ni dung tm tt:
a) L do chn ti
Trong nhng nm gn y, cc m hnh trin khai Internet vn vt (IoT) ang ngy
cng tr nn ph bin, cng ngh IoT l xng sng trong rt nhiu ng dng nh:
ta nh thng minh, thnh ph thng minh, nh my thng minh, nng nghip
thng minh Quan trc mi trng l mt bi ton tiu biu, xut hin trong hu
ht cc ng dng k trn. Trong thc t, cc h thng quan trc mi trng c vai
tr quan trng cc c quan, t chc thc hin gim st, nh gi cht lng mi
trng, t a ra cc d bo v tc ng ca mi trng, phc v cho cc lnh
vc: sc khe cng ng, d bo thi tit v cnh bo thin tai, gim st hot ng
cng nghip, h tr sn xut nng nghip y s l bi ton l tng trin
khai p dng cc cng ngh IoT.
S lng cc thit b kt ni vo mng Internet vn ang lin tc tng ln tng
ngy, cng vi cc kch bn, cc tnh hung ng dng cng ngh IoT cng m
rng khng ngng v ngy cng a dng. Cc doanh nghip v nh pht trin u
mong mun c th ti u c thi gian, chi ph khi tin hnh xy dng gii php
v trin khai cho mt bi ton IoT mi. iu ny t ra nhu cu cn phi c mt
gii php nn tng (mt platform) chung c th pht trin nhiu ng dng IoT
khc nhau da trn , thay v phi lin tc thay i cng ngh.
b) Mc ch nghin cu ca lun vn, i tng, phm vi nghin cu
Mc tiu nghin cu ca lun vn ny l pht trin mt h thng gii php mang
tnh nn tng, c th tng thch v p dng c cho nhiu bi ton IoT khc
nhau. H thng c xy dng cn phi m bo hot ng hiu qu, tin cy, c
th d dng m rng v ty bin. Sau khi xy dng c gii php tng th, mc
tiu tip theo s l thc hin p dng, trin khai cho mt bi ton c th v tiu
biu, l bi ton quan trc mi trng. T cc nh pht trin c th tham
chiu v gii quyt cc bi ton IoT khc mt cch tng t.
Vi mc tiu xy dng mt gii php nn tng, ti s thc hin hai nhim v
chnh:
- Th nht: pht trin mt IoT platform cho php tng tc vi cc thit b
IoT qua cc giao thc khc nhau mt cch an ton, cung cp cc chc nng
h tr t ng ha quy trnh thu thp, x l, lu tr d liu; cc chc nng
qun l ngi dng, qun l thit b v qun l d n.
- Th hai: pht trin mt thit b IoT Data Logger c th giao tip vi cc
thit b hin trng, thc hin thu thp d liu t cc cm bin qua cng
Modbus v cc u vo s, v iu khin cc c cu chp hnh qua cc u
ra r-le, ng thi c th kt ni mng truyn thng vi pha server qua
Ethernet hoc Wifi.
Vi mc tiu trin khai cho h thng quan trc mi trng, ti s minh ha, th
nghim gii php trn h thng quan trc cht lng khng kh, thc hin theo di
cc ch s nhit , m, nng kh carbon dioxide (CO
2
) , nng bi mn
(PM
10
, PM
2.5
).
c) Tm tt c ng cc ni dung chnh v ng gp mi ca tc gi
hon thnh cc mc tiu, nhim v t ra, lun vn thc hin cc ni dung
nghin cu nh sau:
- Nghin cu, tm hiu cc nn tng IoT Cloud Platform ph bin ca AWS,
Azure v Google. Thc hin phn tch v rt ra cc c trng v tnh nng
v kin trc ca mt IoT platform.
- xut thit k kin trc h thng ca mt IoT platform ring.
- Nghin cu, la chn cc cng ngh mi, ph hp thc hin pht trin
IoT platform nh: kin trc microservices, dch v trao i tin nhn phn
tn theo c ch publish/subscribe, phng thc giao tip qua gRPC, phng
php xc thc da trn token, c s d liu chui thi gian.
- Thc hin pht trin cc dch v pha back-end ca IoT platform bao gm:
dch v xc thc, dch v qun l ngi dng, dch v qun l thit b v
d n, dch v giao thc HTTP, dch v giao thc MQTT, dch v thu thp
d liu, dch v truy xut d liu.
- Thc hin pht trin giao din ngi dng (front-end) ca IoT platform.
- Nghin cu nn tng chip ESP32, giao thc truyn thng Modbus, h iu
hnh thi gian thc pht trin thit b IoT Data Logger.
- xut thit k hardware v thit k firmware ca thit b IoT Data Logger.
- Thc hin pht trin, hon thin mt sn phm thit b IoT Data Logger.
- Nghin cu bi ton quan trc khng kh, tm hiu cc loi cm bin o cht
lng khng kh.
- Xy dng, th nghim v nh gi hot ng ca h thng quan trc khng
kh.
d) Phng php nghin cu
Trong qu trnh thc hin lun vn, s dng cc phng php nghin cu sau:
- Phng php thu thp s liu
- Phng php phn tch v tng hp
- Phng php thc nghim
e) Kt lun
Sau qu trnh nghin cu, pht trin v th nghim, lun vn cho thy cc kt
qu tch cc, hon thnh c c bn cc mc tiu t ra ban u. Cc gii php
c xy dng sau khi p dng, trin khai cho bi ton quan trc mi trng
cho thy kh nng hot ng hiu qu, n nh v tin cy. Cc kt qu ny cho
thy vic ng dng thnh cng cc cng ngh mi vo x l bi ton IoT trong
thc t.
Da trn b gii php nn tng m ti ny cung cp, cc nh pht trin c th
d dng to dng cc d n IoT khc nhau ca ring mnh, tng t nh cch
trin khai minh ha trn bi ton quan trc mi trng. Ngoi ra, vi vic lm ch
cng ngh, cng vi s linh hot ca nn tng, cc nh pht trin hon ton c th
thc hin ty bin hay m rng tnh nng, ph hp c vi c cc bi ton
mi hay c th. Ni chung, cc gii php nn tng ny s gip tit kim rt nhiu
v thi gian v chi ph cho doanh nghip v nh pht trin trong vic gii quyt
cc bi ton IoT trong thc t.
